### Corporate Account Management ###

### Get all corporate accounts (paginated)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/corporate?page=0&size=10
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get corporate account by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/corporate/{{id}}
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Create new corporate account
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/corporate
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "name": "New Enterprise Corp",
  "purchases": 55000.00,
  "numberOfOrdersPlaced": 30
}

### Update corporate account
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/corporate/{{id}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "name": "Updated Enterprise Corp",
  "purchases": 65000.00,
  "numberOfOrdersPlaced": 35
}

### Delete corporate account (soft delete)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/corporate/{{id}}
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get all registered corporate accounts
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/corporate?page=0&size=20
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get corporate account 1 details
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/corporate/1
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get corporate account 3 details with all information
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/corporate/3
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get all corporate accounts with advanced pagination
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/corporate?page=0&size=5&sort=dateOfJoined,desc
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
